text:
Yeah, I'm trying to arrange a meeting date, but the
day the other party is offering on Tenka's day off.

If we miss this opportunity, the next one will be
much further away, so... what should I do...

...A day off...
I don't need it...!

Yeah...! Tenka... wants to...
work hard... for the unit live...!

So... Tenka... wants to change...!
Little by little, but... I want to change...!

...Thank you, Tenka-chan.
We're supporting you too... right, Amana-chan?

...! Yeah...!
Amana will support you a lot, Tenka-chan!

Then, Tenka, I'm sorry, but
I'll have to schedule it...

...Huh, what's wrong? Let's do our
best for the unit live, everyone! ...Hehe.
